<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I've set <em>arg_separator.output</em> to {{&amp;amp;}}.
{{http_build_query()}} by default uses this separator in the query strings it builds. This results in HTTP requests like <em>GET /index.php?arg=pie&amp;amp;oh=no</em>.
Most HTTP servers don't understand that and bugger out.</p>

